deepin-water-reminder (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New features:
  * Fun quote display during reminders (18 quotes, Fisher-Yates shuffle).
  * 2 new animation themes: BambooRain (竹林听雨), CherryBlossom (落樱缤纷).
  * Daily drinking goal setting (4-12 cups) with progress bar.
  * Desktop notification fallback when animation fails.
  * Custom reminder message support.
  * Sound effects for reminders (toggleable).
  * Added test coverage for new settings.
  * Full unit test suite now 100% passing (3/3 tests, 22+ cases).

 -- Deepin Developer <developer@deepin.org>  Tue, 30 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0800

deepin-water-reminder (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Fun and non-intrusive desktop water drinking reminder.
  * Features skeleton dance, lion jump, and more animations.
  * Full system tray integration with customizable intervals.

